headline: Camden: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: HOUSTON (AP) — Camden Property Trust (CPT) on Thursday reported a key measure of profitability in its first quarter. The results surpassed Wall Street expectations. The real estate investment trust, based in Houston, said it had funds from operations of $189.8 million, or $1.72 per share, in the period.
